Highlights from BBNaija season 5 tagged The Lockdown will start airing from Monday, March 1 till Friday, March 26, 2021, on Africa Magic Urban and Africa Magic Family at 10 pm. Viewers and the audience of the BBNaija reality TV show will have another opportunity to relive some of the best moments of the Lockdown edition. MultiChoice Nigeria is bringing back the experience six months after the epic grand finale which saw Olamilekan “Laycon” Agbeleshebioba emerge as the winner. The highlights episodes will also get fans primed and excited for the upcoming Reunion show of the season. Viewers of the reality TV show will enjoy up to 40 episodes, containing favourite and most memorable moments from the Lockdown edition. BBNaija continues to be a TV phenomenon in Nigeria and across Africa. The Lockdown edition set the record for the number of votes cast with 900 million votes recorded during the show and over 60 billion impressions on digital. The edition also broke the Showmax live-streaming record, becoming the most-watched live entertainment content ever on the streaming service.